Class GenericDAORestImpl<T extends AbstractModel,PK extends java.io.Serializable>

  • java.lang.Object
    • dao.GenericDAORestImpl<T,PK>
  • Type Parameters:
    T -
    PK -
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    GenericDAO<T,PK>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    EEPPITaskPropertyDAORestImpl, EEPPITaskTemplateDAORestImpl

    public class GenericDAORestImpl<T extends AbstractModel,PK extends java.io.Serializable>
extends java.lang.Object
implements GenericDAO<T,PK>
    Concrete implementation of a GenericDAO. The model is still generic and can be concretised with dependency injection. Is annotated with Singleton, which makes sure the DI framework creates only one instance of the class.
    Author:
    cbi
